# Vercel Environment Variables Configuration
# Add these to your Vercel project settings at: https://vercel.com/dashboard/project-name/settings/environment-variables

# Stripe Configuration
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_or_test_key_here
STRIPE_PRICE_ID=price_1234567890_your_actual_price_id
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_your_webhook_secret_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to your Stripe Dashboard -> Products and create a new product
# 2. Make sure to set it as a "Recurring" subscription (not one-time payment)  
# 3. Copy the Price ID and paste it as STRIPE_PRICE_ID
# 4. Copy your secret key from Stripe Dashboard -> Developers -> API Keys
# 5. For webhook secret: Create a webhook endpoint in Stripe Dashboard -> Developers -> Webhooks
#    - Endpoint URL: https://your-domain.com/api/webhook
#    - Select events: checkout.session.completed, customer.subscription.created, customer.subscription.updated, customer.subscription.deleted, invoice.payment_succeeded, invoice.payment_failed
#    - Copy the webhook signing secret and paste it as STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET

# Example values (replace with your actual values):
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_51Gq...
# STRIPE_PRICE_ID=price_1QF7WOEhwCMl2I7Tc9qzSDfr
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_1234...